CARDSHARP: Cheating at cards undetected

Category: Rogue
Base skill: 24% (+4%/level, cap 98%)

Manipulating a deck of cards well enough to cheat without getting
caught: dealing from the bottom, marking cards, palming a card in or
out of play. Popular among gamblers, con artists, and anyone who
needs to win a card game they should not be winning.

NOTES:
  No AetherMUD command currently rolls this skill directly. It is
  available for character concept and staff-adjudicated roleplay.

SEE ALSO: skills, palming, gambling
